Cell["\<\
Calculate the logarithmic negativity (LN) between the first and second halves \
of the system:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1847549236,ExpressionUUID->"98e49d95-1927-4f3b-b61c-25346ff1e62b"],

